# Create an Nginx instance in AWS using Terraform

ref 
https://awstip.com/how-to-create-an-nginx-instance-in-aws-using-terraform-feb6af12749a

## Commands

```
$ terraform init // initialise terraform
$ terraform fmt // format the code
$ terraform plan // This will show you what resources terraform will create
$ terraform apply // This will create all the resources in your AWS account
```